    "result": {"data":{"post":{"id":"cG9zdDoxODI=","excerpt":"<p>. . . Pada bagian kedua ini akan membahas cara membuat garis dan memprogram aturan permainannya. Buat yang belum lihat bagian pertama, sok langsung ke sini [Link]. E. Menggambar Garis 1. Buat Canvas baru dengan cara klik kanan &gt; UI &gt; Canvas dan beri nama &#8220;Draw Canvas&#8221;. Kemudian dalam &#8220;Draw Canvas&#8221; buat UI Image baru [&hellip;]</p>\n","content":"\n<p>. . .</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pada bagian kedua ini akan membahas cara membuat garis dan memprogram aturan permainannya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Buat yang belum lihat bagian pertama, sok langsung ke sini <a href=\"https://siannas.github.io/blog/2022/12/22/happy-glass-clone-pt-1/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://siannas.github.io/blog/2022/12/22/happy-glass-clone-pt-1/\">[Link]</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-large-font-size\">E. Menggambar Garis</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Buat Canvas baru dengan cara <em>klik kanan &gt; UI &gt; Canvas</em> dan beri nama &#8220;Draw Canvas&#8221;. Kemudian dalam &#8220;Draw Canvas&#8221; buat UI Image baru dengan cara <em>klik kanan &gt; UI &gt; Image</em> dan beri nama &#8220;Touch Area&#8221;.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><span class=\"wp-image-183 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:284px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:94.36619718309859%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/23e11/image-23.png 71w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/efde3/image-23.png 142w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/6a62f/image-23.png 284w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px\" srcSet=\"/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/23e11/image-23.png 71w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/efde3/image-23.png 142w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/6a62f/image-23.png 284w\" src=\"/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/6a62f/image-23.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/23e11/image-23.png 71w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/efde3/image-23.png 142w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/6a62f/image-23.png 284w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px\" srcset=\"/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/23e11/image-23.png 71w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/efde3/image-23.png 142w,\n/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/6a62f/image-23.png 284w\" src=\"/static/a269eb0d6f0bc57c1eec9ae36f1336b3/6a62f/image-23.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Posisikan &#8220;Touch Area&#8221; supaya menutupi keseluruhan layar dan atur mode <em>strect-</em>nya sesuai pada gambar ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><span class=\"wp-image-185 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:585px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:74.65753424657534%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/7b9da/Untitled-13.png 146w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/8890b/Untitled-13.png 293w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/1f316/Untitled-13.png 585w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" srcSet=\"/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/7b9da/Untitled-13.png 146w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/8890b/Untitled-13.png 293w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/1f316/Untitled-13.png 585w\" src=\"/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/1f316/Untitled-13.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/7b9da/Untitled-13.png 146w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/8890b/Untitled-13.png 293w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/1f316/Untitled-13.png 585w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" srcset=\"/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/7b9da/Untitled-13.png 146w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/8890b/Untitled-13.png 293w,\n/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/1f316/Untitled-13.png 585w\" src=\"/static/8f1131ddd1dcaa212de26fda2b4d8a96/1f316/Untitled-13.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>3. Atur layer &#8220;Touch Area&#8221; menjadi &#8220;UI&#8221; dan ubah alpha <em>color</em>-nya menjadi 0.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><span class=\"wp-image-189 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:533px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:130.82706766917292%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/73235/Untitled-14.png 133w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/7afba/Untitled-14.png 267w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/05dcd/Untitled-14.png 533w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" srcSet=\"/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/73235/Untitled-14.png 133w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/7afba/Untitled-14.png 267w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/05dcd/Untitled-14.png 533w\" src=\"/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/05dcd/Untitled-14.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/73235/Untitled-14.png 133w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/7afba/Untitled-14.png 267w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/05dcd/Untitled-14.png 533w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" srcset=\"/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/73235/Untitled-14.png 133w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/7afba/Untitled-14.png 267w,\n/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/05dcd/Untitled-14.png 533w\" src=\"/static/8b3b3ce814b661fbbdd1bc164d0013ff/05dcd/Untitled-14.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>4. buat material hitam di folder &#8220;Materials&#8221; dengan cara klik kanan &gt; <em>Create &gt; Material </em>karena line yang kita gambar memerlukan sebuah material hitam. Beri nama material tersebut &#8220;Line&#8221;. Ubah atribut shader pada material menjadi &#8220;unlit/color&#8221; dan ganti warna menjadi hitam.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><span class=\"wp-image-191 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:690px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:35.838150289017335%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/521fb/Untitled-15.png 173w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/90816/Untitled-15.png 345w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/86e67/Untitled-15.png 690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" srcSet=\"/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/521fb/Untitled-15.png 173w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/90816/Untitled-15.png 345w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/86e67/Untitled-15.png 690w\" src=\"/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/86e67/Untitled-15.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/521fb/Untitled-15.png 173w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/90816/Untitled-15.png 345w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/86e67/Untitled-15.png 690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" srcset=\"/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/521fb/Untitled-15.png 173w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/90816/Untitled-15.png 345w,\n/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/86e67/Untitled-15.png 690w\" src=\"/static/7bec24f7b3c0503e07ea2086e33504d9/86e67/Untitled-15.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>5. Buat script baru pada folder &#8220;<strong>Scripts</strong>&#8221; dengan cara klik kanan &gt;&nbsp;<em>Create &gt; C#-Script</em>. Ubah nama skripnya menjadi &#8220;LineDrawer&#8221;. Klik 2x pada script tersebut dan salin program berikut ke dalam skrip yang baru dibuat. Skrip ini memiliki kegunaan untuk menggambar garis.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>using System.Collections;\nusing System.Collections.Generic;\nusing UnityEngine;\n\nusing UnityEngine.EventSystems;// Required when using Event data.\nusing UnityEngine.Events;\n\npublic class LineDrawer : MonoBehaviour, IPointerDownHandler, IPointerUpHandler\n{\n    public Material LineMat;\n\n    private bool isDrawing = false;\n\n    private GameObject LineGO;\n\n    private LineRenderer LR;\n\n    private int currentIndex = 0;\n\n    private Vector3 pointerPosition;\n    \n    private Camera cam;\n\n\n    // Start is called before the first frame update\n    private void Start()\n    {\n        cam = Camera.main;\n    }\n\n    /// &lt;note&gt; \n    /// Untuk menambahkan Collider dan Rigidbody2D pada line yang akan dibuat\n    /// &lt;/note&gt;\n    private void GenerateCollider(LineRenderer lr)\n    {\n        Mesh mesh = new Mesh();\n\n        try\n        {\n            lr.BakeMesh(mesh, cam, false);\n        }\n        catch(System.Exception e)\n        {\n            return;\n        }\n        \n        PolygonCollider2D collider = LineGO.AddComponent&lt;PolygonCollider2D&gt;();\n\n        collider.pathCount = mesh.triangles.Length/3;\n\n        for(int i=0; i&lt;mesh.triangles.Length/3; i++)\n        {\n            Vector2&#91;] points = new Vector2&#91;3];\n\n            for(int j=0; j&lt;3; j++)\n            {\n                int index = mesh.triangles&#91;i*3+j];\n                points&#91;j] = mesh.vertices&#91;index];\n            }\n\n            collider.SetPath(i, points);\n        }\n\n        Rigidbody2D rb2d = LineGO.AddComponent&lt;Rigidbody2D&gt;();\n\n        /// &lt;note&gt; Buat agar lebih berat &lt;/note&gt;\n        rb2d.mass = 10f;\n    }\n\n    //Do this when the mouse is clicked over the selectable object this script is attached to.\n    public void OnPointerDown(PointerEventData eventData)\n    {\n        pointerPosition = Input.mousePosition;\n\n        LineGO = new GameObject();\n\n        LR = LineGO.AddComponent&lt;LineRenderer&gt;();\n\n        LR.alignment = LineAlignment.TransformZ;\n        \n        LR.startWidth = 0.2f;\n\n        LR.sharedMaterial = LineMat;\n\n        LR.useWorldSpace = false;\n\n        isDrawing = true;\n    }\n\n    //Do this when the mouse click on this selectable UI object is released.\n    public void OnPointerUp(PointerEventData eventData)\n    {\n        isDrawing = false;\n\n        GenerateCollider(LR);\n\n        currentIndex = 0;\n    }\n\n    private void Update() \n    {\n        if(isDrawing == false) return;\n\n        Vector3 dist = pointerPosition - Input.mousePosition;\n\n        float Distance_SqrMag = dist.magnitude;\n\n        if(Distance_SqrMag &lt;= 10f ) return;\n\n        Vector3 worldPos = cam.ScreenToWorldPoint(pointerPosition);\n\n        worldPos.z = 0;\n\n        LR.SetPosition(currentIndex,  worldPos);\n\n        pointerPosition = Input.mousePosition;\n\n        currentIndex++;\n\n        LR.positionCount = currentIndex + 1;\n\n        worldPos = cam.ScreenToWorldPoint(pointerPosition);\n\n        worldPos.z = 0;\n\n        LR.SetPosition(currentIndex,  worldPos);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p> 6. Pada objek &#8220;Touch Area&#8221;, tambahkan komponen skrip &#8220;Line Drawer&#8221;. Masukkan Material &#8220;Line&#8221; ke attribut <em>Line Mat</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"429\" height=\"276\" src=\"/static/cfc027efb80af9a773ef9289118ff380/image-24.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-193\" srcset=\"/static/cfc027efb80af9a773ef9289118ff380/image-24.png 429w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-24-300x193.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 429px) 100vw, 429px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>7. Waktunya tes menggambar. Hasilnya akan mirip cuplikan di bawah ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/static/9a6e745457bdad86008c5ab84b035943/draw.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-250\" width=\"212\" height=\"377\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-large-font-size\">F. Game Manager</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Pertama desain level menjadi tantangan sederhana serupa posisi gelas dan pipa pada gambar di bawah ini. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"313\" height=\"550\" src=\"/static/e4e22ac5188bdd8b67bc5b3121972437/image-25.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-196\" srcset=\"/static/e4e22ac5188bdd8b67bc5b3121972437/image-25.png 313w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-25-171x300.png 171w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 313px) 100vw, 313px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Atur <em>mass</em> pada gelas menjadi <strong>30</strong>  agar tidak gampang terseret air.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"427\" height=\"382\" src=\"/static/4f3906fa312668f168d093fb1cbc4c3d/Untitled-16.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-198\" srcset=\"/static/4f3906fa312668f168d093fb1cbc4c3d/Untitled-16.png 427w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Untitled-16-300x268.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 427px) 100vw, 427px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>3. Atur <em>mass</em> pada <em>prefab</em> &#8220;water&#8221; menjadi <strong>0.1</strong>  agar lebih ringan.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"423\" height=\"507\" src=\"/static/966e8c51443f7a102fe4c0b8dad9561b/Untitled-17.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-201\" srcset=\"/static/966e8c51443f7a102fe4c0b8dad9561b/Untitled-17.png 423w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Untitled-17-250x300.png 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>4. Pada folder &#8220;Scripts&#8221; buat skrip baru dan dengan cara klik kanan &gt;&nbsp;<em>Create &gt; C#-Script</em>. Ubah nama skripnya menjadi &#8220;GameManager&#8221;. Klik 2x pada script tersebut dan salin program berikut ke dalam skrip yang baru dibuat. </p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>using System.Collections;\nusing System.Collections.Generic;\nusing UnityEngine;\n\npublic class GameManager : MonoBehaviour\n{\n    private Pipe pipe;\n\n    private LineDrawer ldrawer;\n\n    // Update is called once per frame\n    void Start()\n    {\n        pipe = FindObjectOfType&lt;Pipe&gt;();\n\n        ldrawer = FindObjectOfType&lt;LineDrawer&gt;();\n\n        ldrawer.drawCallback.AddListener(OnDrawSuccess);\n    }\n\n    // Start is called before the first frame update\n    private void OnDrawSuccess()\n    {\n        ldrawer.gameObject.SetActive(false);\n\n        pipe.StartPipe();\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>5. Jika menemukan error tidak perlu panik, karena akan diperbaiki pada langkah-langkah berikutnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1007\" height=\"156\" src=\"/static/9fe27175785882656fbbc87ec9ed5c10/image-26.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-206\" srcset=\"/static/9fe27175785882656fbbc87ec9ed5c10/image-26.png 1007w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-26-300x46.png 300w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-26-768x119.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1007px) 100vw, 1007px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>6. Pada skrip &#8220;Pipe&#8221;, ubah penamaan method <em>start </em>menjadi <em>StartPipe</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>\n...\n\n    // Start is called before the first frame update\n    // void Start()\n    public void StartPipe()\n    {\n        StartCoroutine(WaitAndSpray(100, 0.05f));\n    }\n\n...</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>7. Pada skrip &#8220;LineDrawer&#8221; tambahkan 1 baris kode berikut di atas tepat sebelum fungsi <em>start.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>...\n    public UnityEvent drawCallback = new UnityEvent();\n\n\n    // Start is called before the first frame update\n    private void Start()\n    {\n...</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>8. Masih pada skrip &#8220;LineDrawer&#8221;, tambahkan 1 baris kode tepat di atas sebelum tanda &#8220;<strong>}</strong>&#8221; / <em>close-bracket</em>  fungsi <em>GenerateCollider</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>...\n\n    private void GenerateCollider(LineRenderer lr)\n    {\n        ...\n\n        drawCallback?.Invoke();\n    }\n\n...</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>9. Maka akan tampak seperti cuplikan berikut ketika di <em>play</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/static/ba64f7e386083c7d94d0c75be01a0c37/draw-on-obstacle.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-248\" width=\"204\" height=\"363\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Nah, sudah terlihat mekanik gimnya hanya perlu memberi aturan minimal air yang dibutuhkan untuk dianggap menang. Perlu dibuat sebuah trigger untuk menghitung air yang masuk. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>10. Buat sebuah trigger sebagai child dari objek <em>glass</em> dengan cara klik kanan objek <em>glass</em> <em>&gt; 2D-Object &gt; Sprites &gt; Square </em>dan beri nama &#8220;trigger&#8221;. Posisikan &#8220;trigger&#8221; mirip pada gambar di bawah ini dan beri warna merah.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"901\" height=\"362\" src=\"/static/60bae91df2cced5163eb060487a4dd5e/Untitled-18.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-214\" srcset=\"/static/60bae91df2cced5163eb060487a4dd5e/Untitled-18.png 901w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Untitled-18-300x121.png 300w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Untitled-18-768x309.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 901px) 100vw, 901px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>11. Pada folder &#8220;Scripts&#8221;, buat skrip dengan nama &#8220;GlassTrigger&#8221;. Salin skrip berikut ke dalam skrip &#8220;GlassTrigger&#8221;.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>using System.Collections;\nusing System.Collections.Generic;\nusing UnityEngine;\n\npublic class GlassTrigger : MonoBehaviour\n{\n    public int count;\n    \n    // when the water collide\n    void OnTriggerEnter2D(Collider2D col)\n    {\n        count++;\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>12. Tambahkan skrip &#8220;GlassTrigger&#8221; ke objek &#8220;trigger&#8221; dan tambahkan komponen  <em>box-collider</em>. Centang juga atribut <em>Is-Trigger</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"378\" height=\"491\" src=\"/static/63ea6c9ef0b997e360d2e765db79472f/Untitled-20.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-225\" srcset=\"/static/63ea6c9ef0b997e360d2e765db79472f/Untitled-20.png 378w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Untitled-20-231x300.png 231w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 378px) 100vw, 378px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>13. Cobalah <em>play </em>dan amati jumlah <em>water </em>yang melewati <em>trigger</em>. Untuk kasus saya jumlah minimum <em>water </em>yang masuk minimal <strong>40</strong>. Namun saya turunkan sedikit sejumlah <strong>37</strong> untuk memberikan kesempatan menang lebih tinggi.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"662\" height=\"390\" src=\"/static/25c0dbbea72a1d86d943575032186e4a/Untitled-19.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-221\" srcset=\"/static/25c0dbbea72a1d86d943575032186e4a/Untitled-19.png 662w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Untitled-19-300x177.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 662px) 100vw, 662px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>14. Kemudian tambahkan teks sebagai tanda gelas terisi penuh. Pada objek &#8220;Draw Canvas&#8221; lakukan klik kanan <em>&gt; UI &gt; Text-TextMeshPro</em> dan beri nama &#8220;Win Text&#8221;. Atur juga tulisan menjadi berwarna hijau dan bertuliskan &#8220;Yay!!&#8221;.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"552\" height=\"356\" src=\"/static/13b875bf206fb67a34f3e376cde1e48e/image-27.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-230\" srcset=\"/static/13b875bf206fb67a34f3e376cde1e48e/image-27.png 552w, http://localhost/blog-wp/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/image-27-300x193.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 552px) 100vw, 552px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>15. Kemudian pada skrip &#8220;GameManager&#8221; tambahkan kode berikut untuk mengecek kemenangan.</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>...\n\n    private GlassTrigger gtrigger;\n\n    public GameObject win_text;\n\n    // Update is called once per frame\n    void Start()\n    {\n\n        ...\n\n        gtrigger = FindObjectOfType&lt;GlassTrigger&gt;();\n\n        win_text.SetActive(false);\n    }\n\n\n...\n\n\n    void Update() \n    {\n        /// &lt;note&gt; 37 is minimum number of water in the glass to win the game &lt;/note&gt;\n        if(gtrigger.count &gt;= 37)\n        {\n            win_text.SetActive(true);\n        }\n    }</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>16. Kemudian pada atribut <em>Win_text </em>di objek &#8220;GameManager&#8221; direferensikan pada objek &#8220;Win Text&#8221; yang telah dibuat sebelumnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><span class=\"wp-image-236 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:629px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:54.77707006369427%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/ae783/Untitled-21.png 157w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/679a3/Untitled-21.png 315w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/2de33/Untitled-21.png 629w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\" srcSet=\"/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/ae783/Untitled-21.png 157w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/679a3/Untitled-21.png 315w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/2de33/Untitled-21.png 629w\" src=\"/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/2de33/Untitled-21.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/ae783/Untitled-21.png 157w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/679a3/Untitled-21.png 315w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/2de33/Untitled-21.png 629w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\" srcset=\"/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/ae783/Untitled-21.png 157w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/679a3/Untitled-21.png 315w,\n/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/2de33/Untitled-21.png 629w\" src=\"/static/d31b5cb1243c1bf1c941c1f197f357b5/2de33/Untitled-21.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>17. Coba <em>play </em>dan hasilnya akan terlihat sebagaimana cuplikan di bawah ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img style=\"max-width:100%;width:162px\" class=\"wp-image-246 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" loading=\"eager\" alt=\"\" src=\"/static/456b20cfdd091379d249c95ca89f9741/final-look.gif\" data-reactroot=\"\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Dan itulah akhir dari tutorial membuat gim serupa Happy Glass. Semoga membantu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Buat yang mau langsung download project bagian final ini bisa di-<em>download</em>&nbsp;di sini&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/siannas/Happy-Glass-Clone/\">[Link]</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Terima kasih sudah berkunjung di blog ini. Apabila ada pertanyaan atau masukan bisa tambahkan aku sebagai teman di&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discordapp.com/users/siannas#6585\">[discord]</a>&nbsp;dan di&nbsp;<a href=\"https://telegram.me/siannas\">[telegram]</a>&nbsp;atau bisa langsung komen di bawah.</p>\n","title":"Happy Glass Clone Pt 2","uri":"/2022/12/27/happy-glass-clone-pt-2/","date":"December 27, 2022","featuredImage":null},"previous":null,"next":{"uri":"/2022/12/22/happy-glass-clone-pt-1/","title":"Happy Glass Clone pt.1"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://siannas.github.io"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoxODI=","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":"cG9zdDoyNA=="}},
